title: Meghan Markle puts her own stamp on the monarchy
text:
Meghan Markle puts her own stamp on the monarchy 10:38am EDT - 01:46
A biography of Britain's latest royal, Meghan Markle, appeared on the monarchy's official website within hours of her marrying Prince Harry, with a single quote: ''I am proud to be a woman and a feminist.'' ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
